dct_title_s: Survey of Palestine 1:100,000 / compiled, drawn & reproduced by Survey of Palestine..
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Contour interval 25 metres. Gridded with Palestine transverse Mercator Military grid. Levant grid in red. Magnetic declination diagram. "Copied from a map by the Dept. of Lands & Surveys, Palestine." Set includes various issues of some sheets, some reissued by U.S. Army Map Service. Most sheets are gridded with the Palestine transverse Mercator Military Grid. Levant grid in red. Shows vegetation types, three types of boundaries, railroads, four classes of roads and tracks, wadis, ruins, and minarets. Includes sheet indexes to old and new series. Geographic coverage complete in 14 sheets. Map library is missing 2 sheets.
